        <Parent_String>input devices [300168267], peripherals (computer) [300024527], computer equipment [300235731], data processing equipment [300125627], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
